Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.92,0:01:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}现在开始我将要充分享受你的悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.92,0:01:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}模拟 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.95,0:01:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}第二十六号机构 贯式闭锁态 铁处女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.78,0:01:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}祸动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.00,0:02:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}第八号机构 碎式圆环态 法兰克王国车轮刑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.47,0:02:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}祸动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.05,0:02:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没错 这正是我期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.25,0:02:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}来吧 发出愉快的悲鸣倒下吧 婊子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.68,0:02:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}关于讴歌悲鸣的方法 你和我有数百年的差距
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.00,0:02:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}哭喊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.74,0:03:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}第三号机构 断式落下态 断头台
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}菲雅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}婊子 婊子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.87,0:03:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}竟敢 竟敢这么凌辱我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}婊子 婊子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.79,0:03:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}杀了你 灭了你 宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.23,0:04:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那是什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.95,0:04:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}总之得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.44,0:04:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}法兰克王国的车轮刑 祸动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}悲鸣 想要听悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.88,0:04:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我就是为此而被制造出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我就是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}回复正常吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}已经结束了 敌人已经跑了 菲雅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}到底在 干什么啊 你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}菲雅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.25,0:04:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}淋雨 这也是第一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}原来 是这么冰冷的东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你想了解的我的真相 就是这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}春亮 她说的话全都是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.78,0:05:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我杀了好几百人 只为杀戮而被制造出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.54,0:05:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以才被诅咒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.54,0:05:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}并且更讽刺的是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为受到诅咒而获得的人的意识
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}学会了罪孽这一概念
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}随处可见的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}哼 也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我的诅咒只是随处可见的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.43,0:05:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一定会让持有者疯狂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.84,0:05:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而变得不停使用我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没错 随处可见的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以说 我不会受到那诅咒的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只要留在这就没问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.03,0:06:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我 从理解到了最根本的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.45,0:06:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我只是盲目地追寻着梦想和希望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}愚蠢到不作任何思考
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一味地想要忘记而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.72,0:06:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那种事根本不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.43,0:06:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}菲雅 冷静点 你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我身负罪孽 杀人 杀人无数的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以才会被罪孽诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.04,0:06:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以 惩罚 惩罚是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}呐 我 真的可以被原谅吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}回去吧 这里太冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你的回答真温柔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.09,0:07:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}最差劲的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}果然我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.14,0:07:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}等等菲雅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.73,0:07:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}菲雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.26,0:07:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没事吗？春亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}春亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}菲雅 菲雅 等等 菲雅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.39,0:07:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}菲雅 菲雅 菲雅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.09,0:07:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}还不能起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}虽然做了紧急处理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}血…流了好多血
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没事的 有好好避开要害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}可能没想像中的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:07:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是 命令式的提案
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}去医院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.03,0:08:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你想说不要去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.90,0:08:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这样的话 想怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.27,0:08:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}会生气的 就算是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,0:08:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}追上那孩子 你要怎办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.23,0:08:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他以自己的意识离开的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而且 那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.95,0:08:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}虽然失去了手臂 但还没放弃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.14,0:08:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我觉得逃走也是好方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.62,0:08:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.26,0:08:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那家伙一个人沉睡会比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.05,0:08:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没有逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而是 找更过分的结束方式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}拜托了 一生的恳求
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}此叶姊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}卑鄙啊 这么叫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不都约定好别这么说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.69,0:09:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为一起做为高中生了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}以前像这样拜托你的话你都会听的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}才不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只是个人自言自语
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.60,0:09:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}大概我想那孩子只是不了解"理所当然"吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.46,0:09:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}非常简单的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.22,0:09:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你听到我的自言自语了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.10,0:09:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}听到的话 就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.68,0:09:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这是她的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.35,0:09:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}罪和诅咒会怎么样的提示
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.45,0:09:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}简单来说 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.71,0:09:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我可没从 春亮那得到答案喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.08,0:09:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那孩子跟我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.42,0:09:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我以前也想过同样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.89,0:09:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}现在的我仍然还是没有找到解答
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.14,0:09:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是 我一直在春亮的家里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:09:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.02,0:10:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}此叶姊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.50,0:10:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}悲鸣 哀伤的悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}滑稽的悲鸣 痛苦的悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}全部的悲鸣都令人怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是道具的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.92,0:10:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}曾是道具的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.87,0:10:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}被用 被雍有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}被需要的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}悲鸣 悲鸣……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.51,0:10:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}证明自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.43,0:10:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}烦死了 烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}住口 别叫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.10,0:10:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.90,0:11:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}菲雅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.02,0:11:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.30,0:11:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}菲雅 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.03,0:11:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}喂 菲雅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.64,0:11:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}烦死了 悲鸣就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这是 第十九号机关
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.55,0:11:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}掘式螺旋态 人体钻孔机
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我 我的其中一个 使用了357次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}还是358次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}最后一个使用人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.14,0:11:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.57,0:11:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我是上野锥霞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.40,0:11:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}学校的班长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.95,0:11:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}住手 菲雅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.31,0:12:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}菲雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}果然还是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.05,0:12:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}菲…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.90,0:12:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怪物绷带
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}开什么玩笑 干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}已经吸饱了 没事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.51,0:12:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}伤口…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.48,0:13:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怪物绷带是活着 所以会吸血
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}为了止住即将死亡的伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.44,0:13:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}会比死亡更痛的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.35,0:13:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这就是这绷带的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.36,0:13:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你就是我的后援吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.93,0:13:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为关系到生命 所以擅自动手了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.95,0:13:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}为什么 擅自的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.69,0:13:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}还可以战斗 那个臭婊子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.52,0:13:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不管几次都要打…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}后援为了让前线的骑士完成使命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}会进行最大限度的支援
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.87,0:13:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}相信那是最佳的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}无谓的浪费生命 我也会被判断成无能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.04,0:13:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}还以为是怎样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:14:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}打开遮蔽物 让我看看脸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.75,0:14:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果是必须的话 那就
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}可恶 到底跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.82,0:14:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我看见菲雅了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在哪边 现在在找他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.60,0:14:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}果然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.94,0:14:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}样子有些奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.11,0:14:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就跟她说些话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.48,0:14:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这样啊 接下来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.48,0:14:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不 没有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}现在她 有些不安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.06,0:14:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}大概 什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}班长 抱歉 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.08,0:14:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不 没什么大事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只是 不知如何说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.85,0:14:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}说实话 我很混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.01,0:14:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}看到不可思议的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.36,0:14:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}菲雅 菲雅手上的魔术方块…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}班长 抱歉 能先忘掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.27,0:14:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.32,0:15:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}后面会好好说明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.53,0:15:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真没办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.52,0:15:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你也有你的苦衷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.65,0:15:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.60,0:15:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}谢谢 班长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.92,0:15:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}证明我存在过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.30,0:15:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}地上满是鲜血
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.11,0:15:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}被用水冲过的血
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.08,0:15:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}血流成河
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.72,0:15:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}然而 冲洗掉那些血的谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.75,0:15:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不停的血
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.87,0:15:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}准备成为新血的谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.81,0:15:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是 我喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只有他对我说出同情的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.90,0:15:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就算现在还记得 残留于记忆中的悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.77,0:15:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}失去了谁 喜欢着的某人的悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那是我强迫着他发出的悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.19,0:16:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}开始的大海吗 为什么想起了从前的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是 开始已经结束了 这也不坏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.51,0:16:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}想起来吧 想起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.59,0:16:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她是什么样的人 在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.28,0:16:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}想起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.82,0:16:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}难道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}什么嘛 比在电视上看到的更加恐怖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.42,0:16:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这可是全黑的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.16,0:16:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}无边的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}简直跟我以前待的地方一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是 为何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.51,0:16:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}会有留恋的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}菲雅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真是的 为何会如此留恋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.29,0:17:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我可是要杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.88,0:17:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他是不会过来追我的 这被诅咒的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}菲雅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}被诅咒的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.80,0:17:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}冰冻的 寒冷的 黑暗的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.21,0:17:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我只是回到只有我的地方而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.42,0:17:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是 比从前更加寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}重要的事情忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:18:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她非常的重 而且是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以躲起来的地方也没想好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那么 就去找她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.87,0:18:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}菲雅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}很温暖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.75,0:18:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你醒过来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.89,0:18:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不过 怎么说呢 跟你的体型不符合啊 超级重
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不要说我重 这是第二次了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.14,0:18:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}第一次是什么时候 啊 你刚来的时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}对女士怎么能说这么无礼的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.07,0:18:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真巧啊 我也很生气 诅咒你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我再说一遍 诅咒你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我的诅咒很灵验的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.77,0:18:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以 不想被诅咒的话就别说话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.91,0:19:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你说“放我下来”或者“别管我”的瞬间 你就会遇到不幸的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.98,0:19:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}会怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.69,0:19:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}胸部就不再长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.63,0:19:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.85,0:19:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}再说 你的诅咒对我是无效的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.88,0:19:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没用 没用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为没用 所以我是不会放你下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}也不会听你的任性要求
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.06,0:19:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就这样把你带回家里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.37,0:19:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}无论怎么样都会把你带回去的 做好觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.28,0:19:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真嚣张 明明只是个不知羞耻的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.30,0:19:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那可真抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.88,0:19:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}哦 怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.59,0:19:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}正好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.37,0:19:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就这样听我说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.26,0:19:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}说话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.89,0:19:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是的 不趁现在的话 我的决心就会动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.21,0:19:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}春亮 我害怕悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:19:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}正确来说 是害怕亲近的人的悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.56,0:20:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}像今天这样 你被别人伤害了而发出惨叫的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.73,0:20:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我又会回复自己的本性了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}要放手的话 就趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.42,0:20:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}为什么说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.65,0:20:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我不知道我是否有留在这里的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.46,0:20:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我是否拥有解除诅咒 失去罪孽的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.35,0:20:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那个 我不知道我有说过资格之类的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.64,0:20:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}想留的话留在这里就行了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.15,0:20:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}重要的是你自己是否想留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.76,0:20:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}即使诅咒不了你 你也别小瞧我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.85,0:20:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我会让你知道我能使用更直接的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.32,0:20:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怎么样 很冷吧 让你好看的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.31,0:20:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这样就给你施加了感冒的诅咒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.63,0:20:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那还真可怕啊 无论是谁每年都会中一次的诅咒
Comment: 0,0:21:11.81,0:21:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.51,0:22:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}哈啾 等等 菲雅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.10,0:22:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好了 你就老实待着吧 我不是说要给你擦背吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.33,0:22:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}别 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.65,0:22:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}别脱我衣服！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.62,0:22:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真的会感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.25,0:22:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.39,0:22:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你们在干嘛 难得上野担心你而特意跑过来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.58,0:22:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我真笨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.77,0:22:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}等等 这是误会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.78,0:22:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}什么误会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.41,0:23:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}确实 这是第一次 不知道能不能做好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.22,0:23:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我会尽量用身体来侍奉你 会让你很爽的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.67,0:23:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我不会再放任不管了 我也一起来干
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.94,0:23:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}第四章 夜晚是母亲和抱枕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.00,0:23:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不看的话就诅咒你喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.19,0:23:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}
